@OpenAgents.OrchestratorApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5236

### Health check
GET {{OpenAgents.OrchestratorApi_HostAddress}}/healthz
Accept: application/json

###

### List jobs
GET {{OpenAgents.OrchestratorApi_HostAddress}}/api/jobs
Accept: application/json

###

### List providers
GET {{OpenAgents.OrchestratorApi_HostAddress}}/api/providers
Accept: application/json

###

### List workflows
GET {{OpenAgents.OrchestratorApi_HostAddress}}/api/workflows
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a job
POST {{OpenAgents.OrchestratorApi_HostAddress}}/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Planning Job",
  "description": "Analyse the workspace and produce an implementation plan",
  "workflowSlug": "planning",
  "providerId": "claude-code",
  "model": "claude-opus-4-5"
}

###

### Get a specific job (replace {id} with a real job ID)
# GET {{OpenAgents.OrchestratorApi_HostAddress}}/api/jobs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###

### Stream job events via SSE (replace {id})
# GET {{OpenAgents.OrchestratorApi_HostAddress}}/api/jobs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/events
# Accept: text/event-stream

